### ============================================================
### 알림 시스템 APIs
### ============================================================

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 알림 목록 조회 (페이징)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notifications?page=0&size=20
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 읽지 않은 알림 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notifications/unread
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 알림 요약 (읽지 않은 개수)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notifications/summary
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 알림 읽음 처리
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notifications/1/read
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 모든 알림 읽음 처리
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notifications/read-all
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 알림 삭제
### ----------------------------------------------------------
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notifications/1
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 알림 설정 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notifications/preferences
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 알림 설정 수정
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notifications/preferences
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "pushEnabled": true,
  "emailEnabled": false,
  "missionNotification": true,
  "guildNotification": true,
  "friendNotification": true,
  "achievementNotification": true
}
